title: SwifTEA: J*ake's Bold Red Move Has Us Feeling Confused
description:
The audacity to drop this photo on us. What a bold move.... but why? Is this just a publicity stunt? The investigation is on!
What do you think is going on? Share all of your thoughts, theories and ideas with us! There are lots of ways to contact us!
